  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 9.24,
      "start_time": 8.47,
      "recording_attendee_id": null,
      "order_number": 0,
      "text": "Hey guys."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 10.97,
      "start_time": 9.9,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 1,
      "text": "Hey, how's it going?"
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 12.19,
      "start_time": 11.77,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 2,
      "text": "Good."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 14.9,
      "start_time": 12.2,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "I'm sorry for the late arrival."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 16.35,
      "start_time": 15.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 4,
      "text": "No problem at all."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 18.21,
      "start_time": 16.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 5,
      "text": "I was uh have you been"
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 20.69,
      "start_time": 20.09,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 6,
      "text": "busy?"
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 21.43,
      "start_time": 20.7,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 7,
      "text": "Honestly?"
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 22.89,
      "start_time": 21.44,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "It's just been insane."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 26.31,
      "start_time": 22.9,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 9,
      "text": "But um I don't know why either."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 27.91,
      "start_time": 26.32,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "I'm trying not to be so busy."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 43.43,
      "start_time": 27.92,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "I think my little guys um started Little League and that's been held in terms of the amount of games and touch points and I'm not even coaching, but I just have to get them places and that's been a, a mess."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 45.43,
      "start_time": 43.44,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 12,
      "text": "But anyway, we're, we're getting through it."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 53.75,
      "start_time": 45.5,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "What, what age is he, man, he quit, you know, the whole thing is like just I've got it, I've got it on the personal and, and professional front right now."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 57.77,
      "start_time": 53.76,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "Lot, lots of, lots of, lots of, lots of going on."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 59.18,
      "start_time": 57.78,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "I, I get it."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 59.85,
      "start_time": 59.19,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 16,
      "text": "I get it."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 61.36,
      "start_time": 60.13,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 17,
      "text": "Uh How old is he?"
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 68.81,
      "start_time": 61.37,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "He's like he's, and he's only 10 but, and my little girl, my little girl just gets dragged around everywhere, I think right now."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 76.11,
      "start_time": 68.82,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 19,
      "text": "But um I feel like 10 is when I really get to go and especially, you know, the little League and the amount of games."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 86.72,
      "start_time": 78.34,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 20,
      "text": "Well, it's like we have four touches a week, um, just without the games and then the half, the team, you know, post Oak Little League is this."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 116.5,
      "start_time": 86.73,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 21,
      "text": "Houston is so intense for, I think because the weather is better and they just expect like, well, it's, it's fine, we can play, we can do this and, you know, this, like, it's so, um, and on top of that, I think over half the, like most of the team has private batting coaches and I mean, it's, it's just, it's, I've never seen anything like this at 10, but I could imagine the Houston baseball scene being pretty intense."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 134.86,
      "start_time": 117.07,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 22,
      "text": "I used to try and coach and then, um, realize that every other dad coach either played college ball or, um, you know, maybe you did it in the minors and I was like, ok, well, we're not doing this anymore."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 142.12,
      "start_time": 135.67,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 23,
      "text": "Um, yeah, so we're just trying to get in, let's, let's do guy."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 146.37,
      "start_time": 142.72,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 24,
      "text": "It's, it's just been kind of a whirlwind and then I've been on the road quite a bit."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 152.75,
      "start_time": 146.38,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 25,
      "text": "And so, you know, I'm expected to do a lot of, um, kid duty when I'm here."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 163.68,
      "start_time": 152.76,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 26,
      "text": "Um, so I think I'm gonna, I may short circuit this a little bit guys just because I'll tell you where, um, we, we landed."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 170.47,
      "start_time": 163.69,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 27,
      "text": "I think this is something that we are willing to, to, we are, well, let me put it this way,"
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 181.57,
      "start_time": 171.5,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 28,
      "text": "some of the other products, you know, we vetted what we're buying through, after talking the last time with Apartment Guide and what we have through their gold package and whatnot."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 187.53,
      "start_time": 181.58,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 29,
      "text": "We know it's not exactly the same because of the touch points in the number of impressions."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 191.13,
      "start_time": 187.54,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 30,
      "text": "But there are some of the profiles that are there."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 195.25,
      "start_time": 191.41,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 31,
      "text": "And right now at this moment in time,"
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 199.31,
      "start_time": 196.28,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 32,
      "text": "our issue isn't a lack of leads."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 201.51,
      "start_time": 199.32,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 33,
      "text": "It's almost lead overload."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 219.7,
      "start_time": 201.52,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 34,
      "text": "It's a lack of follow up and qualified leads and, but, but that said, um I know you guys had AAA kind of a sweetheart offer at the end of last year, which was like 100 bucks, uh uh community per month."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 241.68,
      "start_time": 220.28,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 35,
      "text": "And I think if you can get, get that, we would be willing to try, you know, a subset of maybe 25% to 30% of the portfolio as a, as a, you know, initial trial basis and then, you know, move on from there if that works for you,"
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 244.14,
      "start_time": 244.12,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 36,
      "text": "how"
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 247.19,
      "start_time": 245.22,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 37,
      "text": "many we have again, Jake, go ahead."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 249.53,
      "start_time": 247.56,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 38,
      "text": "We're about 15 properties."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 252.83,
      "start_time": 249.54,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 39,
      "text": "So it'd be like th like 13 or so properties."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 263.35,
      "start_time": 252.94,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 40,
      "text": "Yeah, 13 to 15 properties we could go forward on and see how it goes across the country and just see what they, what that looks like."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 268.93,
      "start_time": 263.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 41,
      "text": "And if it, you know, really is killing it, obviously, we would"
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 284.64,
      "start_time": 269.97,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 42,
      "text": "expand it and if it's not, um we would kill it, but it's foot in the door and it's, you know, um just a way that we think might be a good initial"
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 288.72,
      "start_time": 286.4,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b2ce16da-2c91-4e97-b867-3f39e787d1e0",
      "order_number": 43,
      "text": "way to get you guys in the mix."
    },
    {
      "id": "92f0e10e-0b6c-4593-9ef1-61c518fe3c04",
      "recording_id": "389d7c39-6abe-4ec3-9d14-63230779a467",
      "end_time": 291.61,
